## mleap_model_schema

## Description
 Returns the schema of an MLeap transformer. 


## Usage
```r
 
mleap_model_schema(x) 
```

## Arguments
|Arguments|Description|
|---|---|
| x | An MLeap model object. |



## Value
 A data frame of the model schema.
